headline: Aflac (AFL): Buy, Sell, or Hold Post Q2 Earnings?
summary: Aflac currently trades at $107.18 per share and has shown little upside over the past six months, posting a small loss of 1.2%. The stock also fell short of the S&P 500’s 22.9% gain during that period.
